'''瑞利·奧普卡'''（{{lang-en|'''Reilly Opelka'''}}，{{bd|1997年|8月28日}}）是一位美國[[網球|網球]]運動員。他在2015年[[溫布爾登網球公開賽|溫布爾登網球公開賽]]上打入男子少年單打的決賽並獲得冠軍<ref name="reaches">{{cite news|url=http://www.news-journalonline.com/article/20150710/SPORTS/150719960/101040?Title=Palm-Coast-s-Reilly-Opelka-defeats-world-s-No-1-junior-reaches-Wimbledon-final|title=Palm Coast's Reilly Opelka defeats world's No. 1 junior, reaches Wimbledon final|work=The Daytona Beach News-Journal|date=July 10, 2015|accessdate=July 12, 2015|first=Chris|last=Boyle|archive-date=2015-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712230429/http://www.news-journalonline.com/article/20150710/SPORTS/150719960/101040?Title=Palm-Coast-s-Reilly-Opelka-defeats-world-s-No-1-junior-reaches-Wimbledon-final|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bigtriumph">{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/jul/12/reilly-opelka-wins-boys-singles-title|title=Reilly Opelka’s big triumph hints at better days for American tennis|first=Simon|last=Camber|work=The Guardian|date=July 12, 2015|accessdate=July 12, 2015|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807010034/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/jul/12/reilly-opelka-wins-boys-singles-title|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

